Package com.winterhavenmc.savagegraveyards.models.discovery

Interface Discovery

All Known Implementing Classes:
InvalidDiscovery, ValidDiscovery
public sealed interface Discovery permits ValidDiscovery, InvalidDiscovery
Represents a graveyard discovery as an algebraic data type, implemented using a sealed interface with permitted types of ValidDiscovery or InvalidDiscovery.
